{"tid":232647,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子買山寨機失千元","createTime":"2017-05-07T01:53:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-07T02:02:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6d0a4ec2a322d05c09871b790278eeca3e796937","tid":232647,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T01:53:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20013505&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170507\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20013505%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170507&d=ZAqn3h4t0e4XfOyVRCtvGP6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=4ba21423\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20013505%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170507&h=840eb017\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20013505&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170507</a><br />\n<br />\n男子買山寨機失千元<br />\n<br />\n要聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】大埔一名男子，前日收工後去買餸，途中遇上一名報稱「輸晒啲錢冇錢開飯」爛賭漢，願以1,000元賤賣手上玫瑰金iPhone 6 Plus手機予他，事主以為「執到筍嘢」，結果被人「搵笨」，購買一部沒法運作的山寨版iPhone。<br />\n遇騙事主姓鄧，年約60歲，在區內經營學校飯盒，女兒惟恐騙徒再次得手，前晚10時許，在facebook「Tai Po大埔」群組發帖，詳述事發經過，希望市民提高警覺，「唔好再上當」。<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n山寨iPhone開機後不能正常運作。<br />\n<br />\n顯示2008年 現簡體字<br />\n<br />\n事發於前日下午5時許，鄧伯收工後計劃往大元邨街市買餸，途中一名年約50歲的男子上前搭訕，聲稱爛賭輸錢，遞給鄧伯一部iPhone手機，指往手機舖放售只能賣上800元，他認為被人壓價，希望鄧伯江湖救急，以2,000元買下。<br />\n雙方討價還價後，最終以1,000元成交，鄧伯將手機帶回家，女兒發現手機問題多多，顯示日期為2008年，出現簡體字，又彈出彩色橫間及少量英文字或數字，完全未能正常運作，鄧伯始知受騙，事後更氣憤得整晚失眠。<br />\n鄧的妻子稱，丈夫見手機有畫面，外殼不殘舊，不像賊贓，「可能佢貪貪哋心，於是就畀咗錢佢（騙徒）」。<br />\n■記者劉雲彪"},{"pid":"2da90337bdba31628a345661e207907b09c31e35","tid":232647,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T01:54:58.000Z","msg":"山寨iPhone開機後不能正常運作。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170507/large/07la5p42.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170507%2Flarge%2F07la5p42.jpg&h=caf28fc3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4f7e3812c7e51e823535ed09809455984194cfae","tid":232647,"uid":8171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T01:58:33.000Z","msg":"貪字得個貧"},{"pid":"eed3e22a4fea2e4cc6ba4ef1fa45474d8aebf602","tid":232647,"uid":31237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T02:01:23.000Z","msg":"戇鳩冇藥醫"},{"pid":"32996d94b54f2c21324d519bc55f1ea1a3010c1f","tid":232647,"uid":1567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T02:02:49.000Z","msg":"得60歲就已經比人叫鄧伯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}